Package de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.melt.matching_jena_matchers.filter.extraction

This package contains mapping extraction approaches as shown in
  • Analyzing Mapping Extraction Approaches - C. Meilicke, H. Stuckenschmidt - Ontology Matchign Workshop 2007 paper
  • Ontology Matching (Book) - Euzenat, Jérôme, Shvaiko, Pavel - section 7.7 Alignment extraction
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    HungarianAlgorithm
    Helper Class for HungarianExtractor.
    HungarianExtractor
    This implementation uses the Hungarian algorithm to find a one to one mapping.
    MaxWeightBipartiteExtractor
    Faster implementation than HungarianExtractor for generating a one-to-one alignment.
    MwbEdge
    Helper class for MaxWeightBipartiteExtractor.
    MwbNode
    Helper class for MaxWeightBipartiteExtractor.
    NaiveAscendingExtractor
    Naive ascending extraction as shown in "Analyzing Mapping Extraction Approaches" (C.
    NaiveDescendingExtractor
    Naive descending extraction as shown in "Analyzing Mapping Extraction Approaches" (C.
  • Enum Summary
    Enum Description
    MwbInitHeuristic
    Initialization heuristic for MaxWeightBipartiteExtractor.
